text:
Superb Nasi Lemak nestled in the corner of AMK industrial estate!

Moo-ping is definitely a standout, super tender meat.

Blue pea rice is fragrant and the egg perfectly cooked.

Will definitely return again!
A hidden gem tucked in an industrial at AMK. Love the Moo-Ping and the Blue Pea Nasi Lemak Rice. Reasonable price. Highly recommended. Will definitely order again :)

Chance upon this shop while browsing for dinner. The food came exactly like photo. Loving their signature dishes, especially the Moo Ping and the blue pea rice (nasi lemak) was good too. Also, their chili was so good.
